    "description": "SPC SHIP v1.1: (muCAPE/1500) × (MU_mr/13.6) × (lapse_700_500/7) × (shear_06km/20) × ((frz_lvl-T500_hgt)/8). All five terms capped at 1.0. SHIP > 1 = significant hail potential (≥2\"), SHIP > 4 = extremely high potential"
  },

